query.comment:
This control strategies observes {rain, w} for optimal strategies.
*15000 max runs in approximately 180 minutes. *Set in options -> statistical parameters the 'discretization step for hybrid systems' to 0.1 to speed up calculation. *Set in options -> learning parameters the first four parameters to 200, 15000, 100, 100 to speed up the calculation.
w: water level height This query shows simulation results of water level.
c: cost considering sedimentation and overflow This query shows simulation results of accumulated cost.
Qout: control for discharge from pond to the stream. This query shows simulation results of choosed controller by the strategies.
O: accumulated time for overflow It this indicator is same as zero, it means there was no overflow.
